room_title: Escape room "Dracula: The Final Hour" by Room Escape Los Angeles in Los Angeles

room_description: Vampires are real. They hide behind their wisdom and experience, but you know the truth. You are a team of government agents chosen to end this threat to humanity. You have just an hour to hunt and stop a vampire to prove your worth. Will you prevail against the undead, or will you become one of them?
